'''大衛像'''（{{lang-en|'''David'''}}）是[[文藝復興|文藝復興]]時代[[米开朗基罗|米开朗基罗]]的杰作，於1501年至1504年雕成。雕像为白色大理石雕成的站立的男性[[裸体|裸体]]，高{{convert|5.17|m|ftin|adj=on}}{{efn|The height of the David was recorded incorrectly and the mistake proliferated through many art history publications. The accurate height was only determined in 1998–99 when a team from [[Stanford_University|Stanford University]] went to Florence to try out a project on digitally imaging large [[Three-dimensional_space|3D]] objects by photographing sculptures by Michelangelo and found that the sculpture was taller than any of the sources had indicated.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://graphics.stanford.edu/projects/mich/more-david/more-david.html |title=See |access-date=2022-04-09 |archive-date=2017-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010043921/http://graphics.stanford.edu/projects/mich/more-david/more-david.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://graphics.stanford.edu/projects/mich/publicity/faq.html#height%20of%20the%20David|title=Frequently asked questions (FAQ)|access-date=2022-04-09|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010043922/http://graphics.stanford.edu/projects/mich/publicity/faq.html#height%20of%20the%20David}}</ref>}}，重约6吨，一個[[佛羅倫薩|佛羅倫薩]]藝術中最受歡迎的主題{{efn|See, for example, Donatello's 2 versions of [[Donatello's_David|David]]; [[David_(Verrocchio)|Verrocchio's bronze ''David'']]; [[Domenico_Ghirlandaio|Domenico Ghirlandaio]]'s painting of David; and [[Bartolomeo_Bellano|Bartolomeo Bellano]]'s bronze ''David.''}}。用以表現[[圣经|圣经]]中的犹太英雄[[大衛王|大衛王]]。原作目前置放於[[意大利|意大利]][[佛罗伦萨美术学院|佛罗伦萨美术学院]]，每年都會吸引約120萬人前去參觀。

由於它所代表的人物的性質，這座雕像很快就成為了捍衛公民自由的象徵，[[佛罗伦萨共和国|佛罗伦萨共和国]]是一個獨立的[[城邦|城邦]]，四面受到更強大的敵對國家和[[美第奇家族|美第奇家族]]的[[霸權|霸權]]的威脅 . 大衛的眼睛帶著警告的目光，注視著美第奇家族居住的[[羅馬|羅馬]]<ref>This theory was first proposed{{citation needed|date=June 2021}} by Saul Levine "The Location of Michelangelo's David: The Meeting of January 25, 1504, ''The Art Bulletin'' 56 (1974): 31–49.</ref>。

